"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li>",
"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"UTD.htm?22/11/22711/abstract/2\">",
"      Tindell K, Garfinkel R, Abu-Haydar E, et al. Uterine balloon tamponade for the treatment of postpartum haemorrhage in resource-poor settings: a systematic review. BJOG 2013; 120:5.",
"     </a>",
